divs: Sighting DetailsI was getting in my vehicle this morning around 4:53 from my car clock which might be off a few mins, i leave that time most every morning to go to work, when i looked up in a mostly clear sky and what i thought was a star was dim then got real bright and then just dissappeared . i didnt see any clouds around it , and it seems to like just turn after getting brighter and was gone. not sure what it was really just thought it was kinda strange as i have never seen a star do that before .
